OL,6,GOfcom is expected to confirm this
OL,7,Gmonth whether it will make changes to
OL,8,Gthe advertising rules on the three
OL,9,Gmain commercial channels.
OL,11,FOver the past year or so, it has been
OL,12,Fconsulting over whether to allow more
OL,13,Fdaily ads on Channel 3, Channel 4 and
OL,14,FChannel 5.
OL,16,FEarlier in the summer it announced
OL,17,Fits preferred course of action.
OL,3,CDecision on PSB advertising rules due
OL,4,Csoon
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
