FL,142,140,8ff,8ff,8ff,8ff
PN,14102
SC,0002
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F141A1694156086
OL,6,FIt was minded to allow the three
OL,7,Fchannels to run as much advertising
OL,8,Fas the other commercial channels but
OL,9,Fplanned to keep the rules which place
OL,10,Ftighter limits on the number of
OL,11,Finternal breaks they can show.
OL,13,FIn particular, one break would still
OL,14,Fbe the maximum allowed in a programme
OL,15,Fscheduled for a 30 minute slot.
OL,17,FSome of the responses to this are now
OL,18,Favailable on Ofcom's website.
OL,3,CDecision on PSB advertising rules due
OL,4,Csoon
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
FL,142,140,8ff,8ff,8ff,8ff
PN,14103
SC,0003
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F141A1694156086
OL,6,FThe views of ITV and Channel 4 are
OL,7,Fparticularly interesting, given that
OL,8,Fthe aim of the changes is to help
OL,9,Fpublic service broadcasters.
OL,11,FBoth favour increasing the total
OL,12,Fnumber of minutes of advertising
OL,13,Fwhich they can run. In practice this
OL,14,Fwould mean 12 minutes of ads all
OL,15,Fthrough the daytime and evening.
OL,17,FBoth also agree the limits on the
OL,18,Flength of internal breaks of 3
OL,19,Fminutes and 30 seconds worth of ads
OL,20,Fshould go
OL,22,FBut then some disagreement emerges.
OL,3,CDecision on PSB advertising rules due
OL,4,Csoon
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
