SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F141A1694156086
OL,6,FITV argued the rules should be eased
OL,7,Fto give the three channels the option
OL,8,Fto run two breaks within a half hour
OL,9,Fprogramme. It stresses it does not
OL,10,Fplan to do this even if the rules
OL,11,Fchange so this seems to be about the
OL,12,Fprinciple.
OL,14,FChannel 4 though thinks the right to
OL,15,Fshow extra internal breaks risks the
OL,16,Fviewing experience so wants the
OL,17,Fcurrent limits on internal breaks
OL,18,Fkept.
OL,20,FIf Ofcom changes the rules, ITV
OL,21,Fbelieves the move should take effect
OL,22,Fstraight away.
OL,3,CDecision on PSB advertising rules due
OL,4,Csoon
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
FL,142,140,8ff,8ff,8ff,8ff
