SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F141A1694156086
OL,6,FChannel 4 wants to wait until January
OL,7,F2025.
OL,9,FThere does not seem to be a publicly
OL,10,Favailable response from Channel 5
OL,11,Fwhile STV seems to agree with ITV's
OL,12,Farguments.
OL,14,FIt will be interesting to see what
OL,15,FOfcom actually decides.
OL,17,FI wonder if a compromise is possible.
OL,3,CDecision on PSB advertising rules due
OL,4,Csoon
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
