PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F141A1694156086
OL,6,FIn particular, the rules on the
OL,7,Flength of internal breaks could be
OL,8,Flifted immediately ` this could mean
OL,9,Flonger breaks within programmes but
OL,10,Fno ads during junctions.
OL,12,FIt's hard to see any reason for
OL,13,Fdelaying this change if Ofcom agrees
OL,14,Fto make it. It would simply give
OL,15,Fbroadcasters more flexibility over
OL,16,Ftheir break patterns and they might
OL,17,Fnot always use it.
OL,3,CDecision on PSB advertising rules due
OL,4,Csoon
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/7
